\fs25\fsmilli12800 \cf4 \super \strokec4 [9]}}\'a0The programme would also broadcast in German on\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ARD_(broadcaster)"}}{\fldrslt \cf4 \strokec4 ARD}}\'a0in 1963.{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Noddy_(character)#cite_note-10"}}{\fldrslt 
