\fs25\fsmilli12800 \cf4 \super \strokec4 [13]}}\'a0Bestime released its Plywood Noddy Jigsaws series in 1957 and a Noddy jigsaw series featuring cards appeared from 1963, with illustrations by Robert Lee. Arrow Games became the chief producer of Noddy jigsaws in the late 1970s and early 1980s.{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Noddy_(character)#cite_note-Games-13"}}{\fldrslt 
